  "title": "Solus Combo System",
  "description": "A plugin for easy creation of complex attack combos.",
  "longDescription": "<p>Solus Combo System is a plugin for Unreal Engine that allows setting up a combo system for attacks in a simple way. It is made in C&#43;&#43; but it is designed to be used with Blueprints, allowing anyone with or without coding skills to easily create a combo system for fighting or action games.</p><p><br /></p><p>Showcase Video: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/bx3gQFnuhrg\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/bx3gQFnuhrg</a></p><p>Example Project: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XfHwpIJgtUoQRbIw1zCW_nVxMVl48Wtw/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XfHwpIJgtUoQRbIw1zCW_nVxMVl48Wtw/view?usp&#61;sharing</a> (Requires the <a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/paragon-khaimera\" rel=\"nofollow\">Khaimera</a> character).</p><p><br /></p><p>This plugin works perfectly for action games with lots of different possible attack combinations, create your next fighting game and easily configure multiple combos using the graph editor.</p><p><br /></p><p>The system handles melee collision detection using Unreal&#39;s physics system with the shape you want (box, sphere or capsule), it also performs a sweep per frame during an attack&#39;s execution for better accuracy.</p><p><br /></p><p>Solus Combo System uses Unreal&#39;s Animation Montage system to setup attack animations using Animation Notifies.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>NOTE: this is not a template and it does not include animations, it requires basic blueprint knowledge to use it, check the example project and the documentation for details on how to use the plugin.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>This system only supports melee combat, it does not support ranged attacks.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>An example game showcasing some of the plugin&#39;s features can be found <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PMf7eptRWRBbMC-pA6T3X4p6DOYupQQB/view?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p><p><br /></p><p>Questions? Feel free to contact me via email or join the <a href=\"https://discord.gg/KcsB82zYQz\" rel=\"nofollow\">Discord</a> server!</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li> Melee collision detection using sweep for every frame during attacks.</li><li> Graph editor to create re-usable combo configurations.</li><li> Weapon equipment to user-defined bones and sockets.</li><li>Easy global configuration setup.</li><li>Made in C&#43;&#43; for better performance.</li><li>Simple physics shape selection for weapon collisions.</li><li>Configurable trace channels for collisions.</li></ul><p>Code Modules: (Please include a full list of each Plugin module and their module type (Runtime, Editor etc.))</p><ul><li> SolusComboSystem [Runtime]</li><li> SolusComboSystemBlueprint [UncookedOnly]</li><li> SolusComboSystemEditor [Editor]</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 0</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 38</p><p>Network Replicated: (Yes/No): Yes</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Win64</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64, Linux</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IpvW3yiiyL53wsXB1onnfYj3T9WE2yc3thHS4mGQyR0\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IpvW3yiiyL53wsXB1onnfYj3T9WE2yc3thHS4mGQyR0</a></p>",
